  category: "MEDICAL INTELLIGENCE",
  excerpt: "Knowing CPR isn't enough. Master the application of CAT tourniquets, wound packing with hemostatic agents, and chest seals to manage massive arterial hemorrhaging in hostile zones before professional evac arrives.",
